Boating without motors is better. Reading is exciting. Visual Art is the best profession.  Nola explored the lakes, by recalcitrant Dispro, Canoe, Kayak and Rowboat. Muskoka's Animals provided inspiration and many subjects for many images over many years. Pictures are the original visual communication tool. Letters are required for words, whether texting, tweeting or even writing a story. ABC Muskoka examines Muskoka through the old-fashioned hand-pulled linocut pictures and challenging descriptive phrases. The pictures and the words come together in new fashioned electronically produced books, miniature hand made art books and original pints.
